import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import vuetify from './plugins/vuetify'
import axios from 'axios'
import cors from 'cors'


Vue.use(cors({ origin: ['http://localhost:8080'], }))
Vue.prototype.$http = axios
Vue.config.productionTip = false

new Vue({
  vuetify,
  render: h => h(App)
}).$mount('#app')
